title: Water temperature data from the Little Bear River, UT
description: This dataset contains time series of observations of water temperature in the Little Bear River, UT. Data were recorded every 30 minutes. The values were recorded using a HydroLab MS5 multi-parameter water quality sonde connected to a Campbell Scientific datalogger.
subject: Temperature
